(enablePrefetching, numRCQEntries).explanation: Enabling prefetching increases memory traffic and requires more request completion queue entries to handle the additional outstanding memory requests;

(enablePrefetching, power).explanation: Prefetching activates additional hardware units and increases memory access frequency, directly leading to higher overall power consumption;

(enablePrefetching, power_pad).explanation: Prefetching increases I/O activity and signal transitions at chip boundaries, resulting in higher pad power consumption;
